  "detailed_description": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1675000/extras/95d28c0f1af2ef66a49dcdea3b21c6ca.poster.avif?t=1740407290\" width=600 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1675000/extras/95d28c0f1af2ef66a49dcdea3b21c6ca.webm?t=1740407290\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1675000/extras/95d28c0f1af2ef66a49dcdea3b21c6ca.mp4?t=1740407290\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><strong>Surmount</strong> is a free-flowing, physics-based platforming adventure where you’ll experience the joys of mountain climbing. Make your perilous ascent through the various handcrafted and procedurally generated challenges of Mount Om, all the while following a silly story with eccentric folks along the way. <br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1675000/extras/624efbcf430a2ae9acb008cb4fa3f8f3.poster.avif?t=1740407290\" width=600 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1675000/extras/624efbcf430a2ae9acb008cb4fa3f8f3.webm?t=1740407290\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1675000/extras/624efbcf430a2ae9acb008cb4fa3f8f3.mp4?t=1740407290\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>Master your own unique style of climbing either alone or with a friend, upgrade and customize your climber to stand a better chance, and maybe just maybe, you'll be the first ever to reach the top!<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1675000/extras/25be33f726b1ed5f2303d9be88ab4394.poster.avif?t=1740407290\" width=600 height=300 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1675000/extras/25be33f726b1ed5f2303d9be88ab4394.webm?t=1740407290\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1675000/extras/25be33f726b1ed5f2303d9be88ab4394.mp4?t=1740407290\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Procedural & Handmade Levels</h2>Be the first to reach the top of Mount Om, the highest mountain in the world. Discover an endless amount of unique climbing routes along the way.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Physics-Based Climbing</h2>An approachable physics-based climbing system that is endlessly replayable and not overly punishing.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Meet eccentric characters</h2>On your way to the top of Mount Om, you'll meet a variety of eccentric characters. All with their own reasons to journey to the top.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Items & Upgrades</h2>Unlock a variety of permanent and equipable items that will boost your stats.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Customize Your Character</h2>Be the most fashionable climber out there by customizing your character's look.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Daily Mountain</h2>Test your skills and compete with your friends in the Daily Mountain challenge!<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Solo or Duo!</h2>Play on your own or tethered to a friend in local co-op.<br><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1675000/extras/95d9fced29996eea90a0aff6068569af.poster.avif?t=1740407290\" width=600 height=300 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1675000/extras/95d9fced29996eea90a0aff6068569af.webm?t=1740407290\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1675000/extras/95d9fced29996eea90a0aff6068569af.mp4?t=1740407290\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>",
  "about_the_game": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1675000/extras/95d28c0f1af2ef66a49dcdea3b21c6ca.poster.avif?t=1740407290\" width=600 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1675000/extras/95d28c0f1af2ef66a49dcdea3b21c6ca.webm?t=1740407290\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1675000/extras/95d28c0f1af2ef66a49dcdea3b21c6ca.mp4?t=1740407290\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><strong>Surmount</strong> is a free-flowing, physics-based platforming adventure where you’ll experience the joys of mountain climbing. Make your perilous ascent through the various handcrafted and procedurally generated challenges of Mount Om, all the while following a silly story with eccentric folks along the way. <br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1675000/extras/624efbcf430a2ae9acb008cb4fa3f8f3.poster.avif?t=1740407290\" width=600 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1675000/extras/624efbcf430a2ae9acb008cb4fa3f8f3.webm?t=1740407290\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1675000/extras/624efbcf430a2ae9acb008cb4fa3f8f3.mp4?t=1740407290\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>Master your own unique style of climbing either alone or with a friend, upgrade and customize your climber to stand a better chance, and maybe just maybe, you'll be the first ever to reach the top!<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1675000/extras/25be33f726b1ed5f2303d9be88ab4394.poster.avif?t=1740407290\" width=600 height=300 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1675000/extras/25be33f726b1ed5f2303d9be88ab4394.webm?t=1740407290\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1675000/extras/25be33f726b1ed5f2303d9be88ab4394.mp4?t=1740407290\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Procedural & Handmade Levels</h2>Be the first to reach the top of Mount Om, the highest mountain in the world. Discover an endless amount of unique climbing routes along the way.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Physics-Based Climbing</h2>An approachable physics-based climbing system that is endlessly replayable and not overly punishing.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Meet eccentric characters</h2>On your way to the top of Mount Om, you'll meet a variety of eccentric characters. All with their own reasons to journey to the top.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Items & Upgrades</h2>Unlock a variety of permanent and equipable items that will boost your stats.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Customize Your Character</h2>Be the most fashionable climber out there by customizing your character's look.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Daily Mountain</h2>Test your skills and compete with your friends in the Daily Mountain challenge!<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Solo or Duo!</h2>Play on your own or tethered to a friend in local co-op.<br><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1675000/extras/95d9fced29996eea90a0aff6068569af.poster.avif?t=1740407290\" width=600 height=300 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1675000/extras/95d9fced29996eea90a0aff6068569af.webm?t=1740407290\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1675000/extras/95d9fced29996eea90a0aff6068569a